(c) Copyright 1991, 1992, 1993, 1994 Bug Free Development

Stocks  is  a  powerful  technical analysis tool used for charting stock 
price  and  volume  data.  Numerous mathematical formulas can be applied 
to  the  data in the form of @{"Studies" link Studies}. These studies are plotted with the 
stock   price/volume   data   to  allow  you  to  forecast  future price 
movements from previous actions.

